U-direct (Internet Banking)

U-direct is an internet banking service that allows customers to conduct financial transactions via the world wide web from their home, office or on the move.

Features

 

  • Account information service
  • Funds transfer service
  • Cheque book maintenance
  • Bills payments service
  • Salary payment service
  • Customizable options

Benefits

 

  • Online real-time
  • Available 24/7
  • Secure and compatible with major web browsers
